---
title: Hot Honey Brussels & Ricotta Flatbreads with Parmesan & Italian Cheeses
description: In our humble opinion, flatbreads > pizza, any day! We know that may sound blasphemous, but stick with us. First of all, the golden, crispy crust is a veritable blank canvas. It’s not beholden to simply marinara and mozz! In fact, ours is topped with herby lemony ricotta, tender shredded Brussels sprouts, cheese, lemon zest, and a drizzle of hot honey. Can your ’za do that?! Yeah, we didn’t think so.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6203c4a92a465d7f3e08ea40-17a42e9d.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/hot-honey-brussels-ricotta-flatbreads-6203c4a92a465d7f3e08ea40-726f2efc.pdf
