  sugar: 16 g
  protein: 27 g
  fiber: 9 g
  sodium: 1130 mg
servings: 2
time required: 30 minutes
author: Michelle Doll Olson
cuisine: North America
course: main course
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/hot-honey-brussels-and-ricotta-flatbreads-6203c4a92a465d7f3e08ea40
